{"tid":450112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美加強入境檢查　中國人怨：我明明有綠卡","createTime":"2017-10-28T00:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T11:04:33.000Z","uid":35790,"like":153,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"aecf6afb75cae1e84d39f5675ca0e51ea9341d66","tid":450112,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T00:10:11.000Z","msg":"美加強入境檢查　中國人怨：我明明有綠卡<br />\n<br />\n2017/10/28 04:14&nbsp;3963<br />\n<br />\n美國當局自周四（26日）起，加強對入境的旅客檢查，除上機前要接受保安查問，入境時的檢查也更為嚴格。有持有綠卡的中國人抱怨，他們入境時不但被嚴查行李、點算身上現金，還被移民官警告，他們每年只在美國留兩、三個月，辦綠卡的意願和實際行為不符合，下次再被發現，就要吊銷綠卡。<br />\n<br />\n持有綠卡、來自北京的趙姓男子表示，早前與妻子入境美國時，被移民官員嚴查。移民官發現他們在過去5年，2人每年在美國停留時間只有兩、三個月。趙辯稱，他的生意還在中國，無法長期留在美國，移民官則警告他，他們的行為說明與申辦綠卡的意願不符，沒有在美國長期居住的打算，如果再被發現，綠卡可能會被取消。被移民官警告後，趙抱怨，他們被嚴查行李，海關人員更特別問他與妻子身上有多少現金，而且更一張張的拿出來點算，整整花2小時才能過關。美國的旅遊業者坦承，之前當局對綠卡持有者檢查沒那麼嚴格，但近日美國加強對入境旅客檢查，持綠卡被檢查也不用太意外。美國海關及邊境保衛局稱，持綠卡者一年離開美國超過180天，同時沒有報稅紀錄，可能會被判定「有意放棄身分」，之前曾有來自中國的綠卡持有者，一年只回美國一星期，就被官員當場沒收綠卡。<br />\n（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171028/640_1ec7e8633191b879a656e8bc1cf7a993.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171028%2F640_1ec7e8633191b879a656e8bc1cf7a993.jpg&h=78d62bd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171028/640_3c270b5ad8effe011e9dffe04895d508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171028%2F640_3c270b5ad8effe011e9dffe04895d508.jpg&h=8acb413f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171028/1230467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171028%2F1230467&d=pphi4WxfPFt3MC%2BZqVzhVviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c89c4da6\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171028/1230467</a>"},{"pid":"45671e6b7355969af454076cfa0dc7f0625ba2c6","tid":450112,"uid":35790,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T00:13:27.000Z","msg":"沒收綠卡<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60d32fbf60de143d700b2bfd842f4dd8221761b","tid":450112,"uid":13592,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T00:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n查實印度都好很多人丫 點解感覺上外國人冇咁排斥<br />\n真係文化問題？"},{"pid":"f55ecdc2e95f05d08cfe6403c603f56e3a989ba8","tid":450112,"uid":51932,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T00:25:33.000Z","msg":"每年得二三個月係美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n死返大陸啦"},{"pid":"8a5bfc25ed6043690df37bf72866ce40b1ee687e","tid":450112,"uid":15815,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T00:32:44.000Z","msg":"你d支那人唔洗講<br />\n一定會一邊逃稅，一邊攞美國褔利🤷🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"d64df5b67778c790adbd400c86bba54a1e4ce27e","tid":450112,"uid":37661,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T00:36:53.000Z","msg":"乜支那人自己返支那唔洗檢查咩？<br />\n<br />\n咪又係呢樣唔準帶，果樣唔準帶，<br />\n<br />\n又唔見你班畜牲屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0c99c45faa65c99d0ca1adf843c0009684c004","tid":450112,"uid":50801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T00:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜支那人自己返支那唔洗檢查咩？<br />\n<br />\n咪又係呢樣唔準帶，果樣唔準帶，<br />\n<br />\n又唔見你班畜牲屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n美國屌完無咩野，大陸屌完俾人屈做反黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3360c538a434053ded73e4bb4ecb64614818641","tid":450112,"uid":45368,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T01:57:28.000Z","msg":"咁唔滿意返中國囉<img src=\"/assets